rows.label: bf07530100_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]*pant* *pant*

rows.label: bf07530100_0015
rows.name: Homuraa!

rows.label: bf07530100_0020
rows.name: Homura!

rows.label: bf07530100_0030
rows.name:
You're too late.
I've already taken everything I needed.

rows.label: bf07530100_0040
rows.name: Shin, what have you done to Homura?

rows.label: bf07530100_0050
rows.name: I already told you, didn't I?

rows.label: bf07530100_0060
rows.name: I just got back what I lost 500 years ago.

rows.label: bf07530100_0070
rows.name: Metsu... how...

rows.label: bf07530100_0080
rows.name: You think I'd die from something like that?

rows.label: bf07530100_0082
rows.name: I am Heaven's Holy Grail.

rows.label: bf07530100_0084
rows.name: Don't underestimate me.

rows.label: bf07530100_0086
rows.name: [ML:undisp]

rows.label: bf07530100_0088
rows.name: I can't believe you fell for it.

rows.label: bf07530100_0090
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]*snarl*

rows.label: bf07530100_0095
rows.name: You did this to her?

rows.label: bf07530100_0100
rows.name:
To think that one who bears the title of
Heaven's Holy Grail would be bound by mere humans.

rows.label: bf07530100_0110
rows.name:
She was desperately trying
to protect her memories with you.

rows.label: bf07530100_0120
rows.name: Well, I erased them all.

rows.label: bf07530100_0130
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Grr...

rows.label: bf07530100_0140
rows.name: She was quite the devoted one, wasn't she?

rows.label: bf07530100_0150
rows.name:
Saying things like
"Don't take away my memories" and all.

rows.label: bf07530100_0160
rows.name:
Sorry for making you come 
all the way to this remote place.

rows.label: bf07530100_0170
rows.name: If you want the leftovers, you can have them.

rows.label: bf07530100_0175
rows.name: Take her home.

rows.label: bf07530100_0180
rows.name: Homura! Homura!

rows.label: bf07530100_0190
rows.name: I'm sorry, Homura, Hikari...

rows.label: bf07530100_0200
rows.name: Just because you were with someone like me...

rows.label: bf07530100_0210
rows.name: Rex...

rows.label: bf07530100_0220
rows.name: Boss...

rows.label: bf07530100_0230
rows.name: Nia...

rows.label: bf07530100_0240
rows.name: I understand.

rows.label: bf07530100_0250
rows.name: Byakko, take care of Homura.

rows.label: bf07530100_0260
rows.name: Understood.

rows.label: bf07530100_0270
rows.name:
What's this?
I thought you'd be crying and lunging at me...

rows.label: bf07530100_0280
rows.name: Have you grown up a little?

rows.label: bf07530100_0290
rows.name: Stupid...

rows.label: bf07530100_0300
rows.name: Eh?

rows.label: bf07530100_0310
rows.name: I was stupid.

rows.label: bf07530100_0315
rows.name: I didn't understand Homura and Hikari's feelings.

rows.label: bf07530100_0320
rows.name:
Though we were destined to follow different paths,
I tried to walk together.

rows.label: bf07530100_0330
rows.name:
A shadow path created by the strong 
light known as Heaven's Holy Grail.

rows.label: bf07530100_0340
rows.name: Blindly walking my own path.

rows.label: bf07530100_0345
rows.name: Homura and Hikari have been walking alone.

rows.label: bf07530100_0350
rows.name: What are you talking about, boy?

rows.label: bf07530100_0360
rows.name: So, I might be stupid...but I've made a decision.

rows.label: bf07530100_0370
rows.name: Oh? What have you decided?

rows.label: bf07530100_0380
rows.name:
Since we're here, 
I'll be the one to listen on their behalf.

rows.label: bf07530100_0390
rows.name: It's obvious, isn't it?

rows.label: bf07530100_0400
rows.name:
I'll defeat you all and go
to Eden together with those two.

rows.label: bf07530100_0410
rows.name:
Hah! Defeat me?
You who couldn't even scratch Shin?

rows.label: bf07530100_0420
rows.name: Besides, I've regained my power as Heaven's Holy Grail.

rows.label: bf07530100_0430
rows.name: [System:Ruby rt=Devices ]Servants[/System:Ruby] will act just as I wish.

rows.label: bf07530100_0440
rows.name: There's no way you can do it.

rows.label: bf07530100_0450
rows.name: I can do it.

rows.label: bf07530100_0460
rows.name:
That thing is just leftovers now.
It's useless to count on it.

rows.label: bf07530100_0470
rows.name: I now understand.

rows.label: bf07530100_0475
rows.name: What those two truly wish for...

rows.label: bf07530100_0480
rows.name: And what I really need to do for them.

rows.label: bf07530100_0490
rows.name: The true meaning of the bond between Driver and Blade.

rows.label: bf07530100_0500
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]!!

rows.label: bf07530100_0510
rows.name:
Everyone...
Lend me your strength.

rows.label: bf07530100_0520
rows.name: To reclaim Homura and go to Eden.
